<div id="pf514f" class="pf w46 h355" data-page-no="514f"><div class="pc pc514f w46 h355"><div class="t m72c xc h163 y2ede ff1 fs36 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meet the </div><div class="t mf7 xc h163 y2cb1 ff1 fs36 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Author of </div><div class="t m75b x5f h163 y2baf ff1 fs36 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This </div><div class="t m3d1 xc h163 y238e ff1 fs36 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Quarter&apos;s </div><div class="t m6a3 xc5 h163 y1dd2 ff1 fs36 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons </div><div class="t mea2 x65 h2d y1a65 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Russell Holt is associate editor of </div><div class="t m258 x70 h4a y1a65 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Signs of the Times. </div><div class="t m364 xc1 h2d y1a65 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He has served </div><div class="t mae8 x5f h2d y1706 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as executive editor of </div><div class="t m31b x43 h4a y1706 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministry </div><div class="t m78b x20 h2d y1706 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and on the editorial staff of </div><div class="t md0e xe8 h4a y1706 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These </div><div class="t m45b x5f h4a y1885 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Times. </div><div class="t me04 x6 h2d y1885 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He began his denominational career as a pastor in Indiana and </div><div class="t me2 x5f h2d y1d8d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Arizona. </div><div class="t m733 x65 h2d yc1c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Elder Holt enjoys getting involved in do-it-yourself projects, read-</div><div class="t ma20 x5f h2d y16af ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing, and studying the American Civil War era. He has written numer-</div><div class="t m88 x5f h2d y1bc2 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ous&apos; articles for religious and secular periodicals. He and his wife, </div><div class="t mcfa x5f h2d y1b8a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Judy, have a son and a daughter. </div><div class="t m3ad x5f h63 y998 ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Blessing of Daily Study </div><div class="t maae x5b h2d y33b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Every day some portion of time should be appropriated to the </div><div class="t mdb7 x60 h2d y6ab ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of the lessons, not merely in learning to mechanically repeat the </div><div class="t m1062 x60 h2d y1932 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">words, while the mind does not comprehend the meaning; but to go to </div><div class="t m257 x60 h2d y1960 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the very foundation, and become familiar with what is brought out in </div><div class="t m616 x60 h2d y17a2 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the lesson. </div><div class="t ma8 x19 h4a y422 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;—Counsels on Sabbath School Work, </div><div class="t m2a6 x62 h2d y17a1 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 53. </div><div class="t mf2 x60 h63 y181d ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daily Lesson Study Pledge </div><div class="t mc6b x4e h15d yb4f ffd fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">❑ </div><div class="t m729 x65 h2d y1679 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As one greatly desirous of improving my knowledge of the Scrip-</div><div class="t m97 x4e h2d y1df9 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tures and of the Lord to whom they point, I pledge to carefully and </div><div class="t m404 x4e h2d y1787 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prayerfully study some portion of the Sabbath School lesson each day </div><div class="t m61b x4e h2d y1695 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the week. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
